    <description>
        <p>taskZen is a free and open source automation software for Wayland!</p>
        <p>Features:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Automate tasks by creating scripts</li>
            <li>Include mouse movements, button presses, commands and much more in your scripts</li>
            <li>Simple GUI interface to create and edit scripts</li>
            <li>Full Wayland compatability out of the box</li>
            <li>Fully Free and Open Source</li>
        </ul>
    </description>

